org.logevents.status

Class LogEventStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.logevents.status.LogEventStatus

  • public class LogEventStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    Keeps tracks and optionally outputs internal messages from Log Events during configuration and usage. Sample configuration (in logevents.properties or as System properties): 
     logevents.status=CONFIG
 logevents.status.SlackLogEventObserver=TRACE
